{"thag3.2:0.1":"Theragatha 3.2 ","thag3.2:0.2":"Tikanipata ","thag3.2:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag3.2:0.4":"Paccayattheragatha ","thag3.2:1.1":"“Pancahaham pabbajito, ","thag3.2:1.2":"sekho appattamanaso; ","thag3.2:1.3":"Viharam me pavitthassa, ","thag3.2:1.4":"cetaso panidhi ahu. ","thag3.2:2.1":"Nasissam na pivissami, ","thag3.2:2.2":"viharato na nikkhame; ","thag3.2:2.3":"Napi passam nipatessam, ","thag3.2:2.4":"tanhasalle anuhate. ","thag3.2:3.1":"Tassa mevam viharato, ","thag3.2:3.2":"passa viriyaparakkamam; ","thag3.2:3.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag3.2:3.4":"katam buddhassa sasanan”ti. ","thag3.2:3.5":"… Paccayo thero …. "}